  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375920/extras/5e1ce24bd84ad112679a8daa9d9b4c40.poster.avif?t=1602771112\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375920/extras/5e1ce24bd84ad112679a8daa9d9b4c40.webm?t=1602771112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375920/extras/5e1ce24bd84ad112679a8daa9d9b4c40.mp4?t=1602771112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375920/extras/31b18e61b91cda3861d26914278cbc45.webp?t=1602771112\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br>Ghost Beat is a rhythm based precision platformer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375920/extras/6b17eb0222639988beb604fefb2049ea.webp?t=1602771112\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rhythm-based Action Platformer<br></li><li>Minimal design<br></li><li>Epic handcrafted levels synchronized to the music<br></li><li>Simply and easy to play but hard to master<br></li><li>Improve your musical rhythm and reflexes</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375920/extras/912a0856777b8793ec6f9a83d0002f6d.webp?t=1602771112\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br>Hi, I'm Sandor Berczi, a solo indie game developer.<br>It's always been a dream of mine to make a video game. <br>Please wishlist my dream project!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375920/extras/efb14c5cffa89